      {
        "key": "逆焰之刃",
        "title": "逆焰之刃",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/d0e27bc7054292e95c673e6f491ff677_4053958865659999505.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素戰技</color>\n造成3點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。每回合第三次使用本技能時，傷害+2。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "黎明",
        "title": "黎明",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/7f35364dc83b6694a3200aae53f6670f_7818726193858846184.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n造成8點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> ，本角色附屬 <color=#ff9999>火元素附魔</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>火元素附魔</color>\n<color=#ffd780>狀態</color>\n所附屬角色造成的 <color=#ffffff>物理傷害</color> ，變爲 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>持續回合：2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素傷害·其一",
        "title": "火元素傷害·其一",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_294743599819144172.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素+</color> <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>融化</color> ：本傷害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>蒸發</color> ：本傷害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超載</color> ：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素傷害·其二",
        "title": "火元素傷害·其二",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_6561662928639372763.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>燃燒</color> ：本傷害+1，召喚 <color=#ffffff>燃燒烈焰</color>\n<color=#ffffff>燃燒烈焰</color>\n<color=#ffd780>召喚物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>結束階段：</color> 造成1點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_2081888945642630150.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "規則解釋",
        "title": "規則解釋",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6474324292056903802.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>物理傷害</color>\n物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。\n<color=#ffffff>持續回合</color>\n每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；\n持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
